cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CR 

This paper deals with automated software improvement for run-time performance, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The use of Genetic Programming also suggests a focus on programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The comparison of different initialisation mechanisms indicates a potential interest in machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the benchmark suite and performance improvements may also be relevant to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
